1. *Ubojica* je prošao kroz selo bez da je niko primetio. (The murderer passed through the village without anyone noticing him.)
2. Policija je zaustavila *ubojicu* pre nego što je uspela da pobegne. (The police stopped the murderer before he managed to escape.)
3. *Ubojice* su izvršili zločin pre nego što su se povukli. (The murderers committed the crime before they withdrew.)
4. Svi su se bojali da će biti sledeći na listi *ubojice*. (Everyone was afraid of being next on the murderer's list.)
5. Suočen sa *ubojicom*, dete je otišlo u suzama. (Confronted with the murderer, the child went away in tears.)